{"title":"我现在是妈妈了","authors":["周晓萍"],"dates":[{"year":1984,"month":3,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我现在是妈妈了（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖南衡阳　周晓萍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小鸟儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小娇娇醒来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是小鸟叫她起床的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不然她怎么也象只小鸟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扯着早霞的衣襟唱个不停呢？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"娇娇唱完了歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便对小鸟说：“小鸟，小鸟，我问你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的歌也是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为妈妈唱的吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的妈妈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也象我的妈妈一样好吗？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是什么事情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使你大笑起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的孩子？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是因为你能象小鸭那样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一摆一摆地走动？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听我说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无忧无虑的孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你可不要太得意了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要知道，人生的路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是很难走的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈走了这么多年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还没走好呢！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}